-v1%20-%20Roatan%20Real%20Estate%20/',0,'revision','',0),
	(169,1,'2017-10-13 22:23:15','2017-10-13 22:23:15','<p class=\"lg\"><img src=\"http://roatanlife.com/photos/beach-small.jpg\" alt=\"Flora.\" width=\"150\" height=\"116\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">Over the past decade Roatan has become a popular relocation, retirement and investment destination. The island\'s tropical landscape, rich marine life and laid-back lifestyle are attracting people the world over. Many people dream of living in a Caribbean paradise and it is possible for many people to live out this dream here in Roatan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">Roatan real estate is as varied as the people considering a purchase. You will find beach and hill lots, homes, investment property and businesses for sale. You will also find in Roatan that the prices are far below those in other Caribbean locations. It is a good time to buy and invest in Roatan as global real estate prices continue to rise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">In Roatan you will find a variety of stores-supermarkets which stock local and international produce. You will find four banks, numerous attorneys, a gym, high speed internet, an international airport and most services you would expect for a Caribbean destination.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">For people considering relocation with families you will find bilingual schools through out the Island and recently a University opened its doors in French Harbor enabling Roatan youth for the first time, the chance to obtain a University Education without leaving the Island.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">On Roatan you will find a public hospital and a private - Wood\'s Clinic. Additional hospitals are also found throughout the country in most major towns. The country\'s best hospitals can be found in the major cities of San Pedro Sula and Tegucigalpa, which are recommended for serious matters, but both the D\'Antoni Hospital and Medicentro in La Ceiba provide a full range of medical services.</p>','Roatan Relocation Information','','publish','closed','closed','','roatan-relocation-information','','','2017-10-13 22:55:01','2017-10-13 22:55:01','',0,'http://roatanlife.dev/?page_id=169',0,'page','',0),
	(171,1,'2017-10-13 22:23:15','2017-10-13 22:23:15','<p class=\"lg\"><img src=\"http://roatanlife.com/photos/beach-small.jpg\" alt=\"Flora.\" width=\"150\" height=\"116\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">Over the past decade Roatan has become a popular relocation, retirement and investment destination. The island\'s tropical landscape, rich marine life and laid-back lifestyle are attracting people the world over. Many people dream of living in a Caribbean paradise and it is possible for many people to live out this dream here in Roatan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">Roatan real estate is as varied as the people considering a purchase. You will find beach and hill lots, homes, investment property and businesses for sale. You will also find in Roatan that the prices are far below those in other Caribbean locations. It is a good time to buy and invest in Roatan as global real estate prices continue to rise.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">In Roatan you will find a variety of stores-supermarkets which stock local and international produce. You will find four banks, numerous attorneys, a gym, high speed internet, an international airport and most services you would expect for a Caribbean destination.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">For people considering relocation with families you will find bilingual schools through out the Island and recently a University opened its doors in French Harbor enabling Roatan youth for the first time, the chance to obtain a University Education without leaving the Island.</p>\r\n<p class=\"lg\" align=\"left\">On Roatan you will find a public hospital and a private - Wood\'s Clinic. Additional hospitals are also found throughout the country in most major towns. The country\'s best hospitals can be found in the major cities of San Pedro Sula and Tegucigalpa, which are recommended for serious matters, but both the D\'Antoni Hospital and Medicentro in La Ceiba provide a full range of medical services.</p>','Roatan Relocation Information','','inherit','closed','closed','','169-revision-v1','','','2017-10-13 22:23:15','2017-10-13 22:23:15','',169,'http://roatanlife.dev/169-revision-v1%20-%20Roatan%20Real%20Estate%20/',0,'revision','',0),
